{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "1c7fbe52-6b3d-4d5d-bb2a-0c3d3776d5f0",
    "name": "CitySec - Auth (Login)",
    "description": "Colección mínima para probar Login y guardar el JWT automáticamente.\n\nVariables de colección:\n- baseUrl: URL base del backend (ej: https://TU-DOMINIO)\n- apiVersion: versión del API (ej: v1)\n- token: JWT (se llena automáticamente con Login)\n\nUso rápido:\n1) Ajusta baseUrl al dominio de Railway\n2) Ejecuta el request 'Login (guarda token)'\n3) Usa {{token}} como Bearer en otras colecciones\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login (guarda token)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              {
                "key": "Content-Type",
                "value": "application/json"
              }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"username_or_email\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"Admin123!\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/{{apiVersion}}/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "{{apiVersion}}", "auth", "login"]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('Login responde 200/201', function () {",
                  "  pm.expect([200, 201]).to.include(pm.response.code);",
                  "});",
                  "",
                  "let json = {};",
                  "try { json = pm.response.json(); } catch (e) {}",
                  "const token = json?.token || json?.data?.token || json?.accessToken || json?.data?.accessToken;",
                  "if (token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', token);",
                  "}"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "https://citysecbackendclaude-production.up.railway.app"
    },
    {
      "key": "apiVersion",
      "value": "v1"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    }
  ]
}
